      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i just don't want to deal with all the tests and stuff if it's just my old age catching up to me. i feel like i know my body and it's just this slight tightness. if i just take an extra puff or two every time i feel it, i'll be fine right? it's not like i'm having a full attack or anything, just can't catch my breath easily. it's fine, right?",
